{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand","slug":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand","title":"The Lemonade Stand","title_ko":"레모네이드 가판대","level":"A2","ageBand":"9-11","coverUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/cover.webp","summary_ko":"더운 여름날 준과 미나가 레모네이드 가판대를 열어 손님들에게 시원한 음료를 팔며 함께 성공의 기쁨을 나누는 이야기예요.","wordCount":188,"stage":3,"collection":"daily","pages":[{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"It is a hot summer day.","translation_ko":"무더운 여름날이에요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"is","charStart":3,"charEnd":5,"startMs":260,"endMs":860},{"word":"a","charStart":6,"charEnd":7,"startMs":860,"endMs":1160},{"word":"hot","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1480},{"word":"summer","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1820},{"word":"day","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2140}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Jun says, \"Let's make lemonade and sell it!\"","translation_ko":"준이 말했어요. \"레모네이드 만들어서 팔자!\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"says","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":420,"endMs":820},{"word":"Let's","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":880,"endMs":1540},{"word":"make","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1740},{"word":"lemonade","charStart":22,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2180},{"word":"and","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2700},{"word":"sell","charStart":35,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2700,"endMs":2900},{"word":"it","charStart":40,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3080}]}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina is excited because she loves cold drinks.","translation_ko":"미나는 차가운 음료를 좋아해서 신이 났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":500},{"word":"is","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":500,"endMs":800},{"word":"excited","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":800,"endMs":1360},{"word":"because","charStart":16,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1900},{"word":"she","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2200},{"word":"loves","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2540},{"word":"cold","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2960},{"word":"drinks","charStart":39,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3320}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"They find lemons, sugar, and water in the kitchen.","translation_ko":"두 사람은 부엌에서 레몬, 설탕, 물을 찾았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"find","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":200,"endMs":480},{"word":"lemons","charStart":10,"charEnd":16,"startMs":480,"endMs":900},{"word":"sugar","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1500},{"word":"and","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2100},{"word":"water","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2200},{"word":"in","charStart":35,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2440},{"word":"the","charStart":38,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2580},{"word":"kitchen","charStart":42,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2720}]}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun squeezes the lemons, and Mina adds sugar.","translation_ko":"준이 레몬을 짜고, 미나는 설탕을 넣었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":1140},{"word":"squeezes","charStart":4,"charEnd":12,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1720},{"word":"the","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1980},{"word":"lemons","charStart":17,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2240},{"word":"and","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3100},{"word":"Mina","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3180},{"word":"adds","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":3180,"endMs":3620},{"word":"sugar","charStart":39,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3920}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"They smile when they taste it because it is sweet and sour.","translation_ko":"맛을 보니 달콤하고 새콤해서 둘 다 활짝 웃었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"smile","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":440,"endMs":1000},{"word":"when","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1260},{"word":"they","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1460},{"word":"taste","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1740},{"word":"it","charStart":27,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2100},{"word":"because","charStart":30,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2560},{"word":"it","charStart":38,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2660},{"word":"is","charStart":41,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2960},{"word":"sweet","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3240},{"word":"and","charStart":50,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3240,"endMs":4020},{"word":"sour","charStart":54,"charEnd":58,"startMs":4020,"endMs":4220}]}]},{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-97-the-lemonade-stand/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-97-the-lemonade-stand-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"They make a sign: \"Cold Lemonade — 500 won.\"","translation_ko":"\"시원한 